highlights.text: The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Die For You - Remix” is the highest at #3.
“Komang” by Raim Laode is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 101 spots at #61.
“TQG” by KAROL G and Shakira is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 317 weeks straight.
